WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.412
Hail Jesus and Mary, dear friends of the Association "Croatia for Life"

00:00:04.412 --> 00:00:08.610
and subscribers of our YouTube channel "Croatia for Life."

00:00:08.610 --> 00:00:14.730
In this video in the series "Who are we?", I will present you the program "Forgiven and Set Free"

00:00:14.730 --> 00:00:19.252
that we have been implementing in our Association since 2016.

00:00:19.252 --> 00:00:25.527
When the "40 Days for Life" initiative was launched, I was the leader in the city of Vukovar.

00:00:25.527 --> 00:00:31.156
More and more women started approaching me who had experienced abortion themselves.

00:00:31.156 --> 00:00:34.451
They begged me to help them in some way.

00:00:34.451 --> 00:00:40.075
I was not familiar with this program at the time, so it was a little difficult for me.

00:00:40.075 --> 00:00:45.324
However, as I prayed a lot and wanted the Lord to provide some kind of program

00:00:45.324 --> 00:00:49.676
that would be based on His word, we came to that program.

00:00:49.676 --> 00:00:52.960
 The program is called "Forgiven and Set Free."

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:56.296
We conduct it in three different ways:

00:00:56.296 --> 00:01:01.759
either women come to spiritual exercises in silence for three days,

00:01:01.759 --> 00:01:04.980
or we conduct it through weekly meetings 

00:01:04.980 --> 00:01:10.172
of which there are 10 in a certain group of women who gather in a certain city,

00:01:10.172 --> 00:01:15.383
or I follow them online, or by phone.

00:01:15.383 --> 00:01:18.322
What is important about this program is that it is intended

00:01:18.322 --> 00:01:21.421
for the healing of abortion wounds that occur in women

00:01:21.421 --> 00:01:26.894
after they have experienced an elective abortion, i.e. an intentional abortion,

00:01:26.894 --> 00:01:32.071
or miscarriage, the loss of a baby in a high stage of pregnancy

00:01:32.071 --> 00:01:35.321
or even in an ectopic pregnancy.

00:01:35.321 --> 00:01:40.226
All these women throughout all these years, since 2016, when we started conducting it in Croatia,

00:01:40.226 --> 00:01:43.837
have contacted us and come to our program.

00:01:43.837 --> 00:01:49.081
What I really like to say is that, since the program is based on God’s word,

00:01:49.081 --> 00:01:51.600
it is 100% effective.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:57.843
During the program application, we have an application form through which women apply to us,

00:01:57.843 --> 00:02:02.609
either through our Facebook page, or through our e-mail,

00:02:02.609 --> 00:02:06.939
or by contacting me directly and declaring that they want to come to the program.

00:02:06.939 --> 00:02:11.432
In the form we have an evaluation question where they say

00:02:11.432 --> 00:02:17.661
what they plan and what they want to achieve with this program, that is, what they expect from it.

00:02:17.661 --> 00:02:22.111
After the program ends, they see again in these questions,

00:02:22.111 --> 00:02:28.600
that is, their answers, that exactly what they came for is what they really got.

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:33.954
The program consists, to share some technical information, of eight different units.

00:02:33.954 --> 00:02:42.608
Here, we consider God’s personality, what God is like, what anger is like, what depression is like,

00:02:42.608 --> 00:02:48.768
whether they have any need for forgiveness, how they can forgive themselves,

00:02:48.768 --> 00:02:51.613
others who participated in their abortion,

00:02:51.613 --> 00:02:55.463
family members who may have persuaded her to do it,

00:02:55.463 --> 00:02:59.354
and some of them even need to forgive God.

00:02:59.354 --> 00:03:02.407
God can handle it. He is a merciful Father.

00:03:02.407 --> 00:03:07.205
What I learned through working with the women in this program is how much

00:03:07.205 --> 00:03:13.200
the Lord is truly full of love, full of forgiveness, extremely full of mercy...

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:18.878
He is pure mercy and accepts them with open arms.

00:03:18.878 --> 00:03:25.757
Women experience healing, restoration of relationships in families,

00:03:25.757 --> 00:03:29.283
 in marriage, with their children,

00:03:29.283 --> 00:03:35.008
because the consequences of abortion that come with them are really, really hard.

00:03:35.008 --> 00:03:39.385
If we know that, according to the World Health Organization,

00:03:39.385 --> 00:03:44.584
around 70 million abortions are performed in the world,

00:03:44.584 --> 00:03:48.000
and that each of them actually damages in some way the seven lives

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:53.047
that participated in it, then we know that there are many, many more consequences

00:03:53.047 --> 00:03:55.422
and that we don’t know anything about it.

00:03:55.422 --> 00:04:00.948
Every abortion directly destroys the life of the child on whom it is performed,

00:04:00.948 --> 00:04:05.700
whether it is the abortion of one child or twins,

00:04:05.700 --> 00:04:09.982
then the mother who suffers severe consequences afterwards,

00:04:09.982 --> 00:04:14.261
the father who possibly did not want the abortion to occur, but it did occur 

00:04:14.261 --> 00:04:16.482
(and such fathers report to us),

00:04:16.482 --> 00:04:22.098
then family members, brothers and sisters who were left without their family member,

00:04:22.098 --> 00:04:24.074
without perhaps even knowing it.

00:04:24.074 --> 00:04:28.233
Then the grandparents, the doctors who performed the abortion,

00:04:28.233 --> 00:04:31.116
the medical staff who participated in it.

00:04:31.116 --> 00:04:34.396
So, the consequences are very big, heavy, destructive

00:04:34.396 --> 00:04:38.525
and, if they are not taken care of in time,

00:04:38.525 --> 00:04:44.617
they can lead to a very, very big discord inside and outside the person.

00:04:53.656 --> 00:04:58.762
The women who came to our program wrote before the program began

00:04:58.762 --> 00:05:02.392
what they were struggling with.

00:05:02.392 --> 00:05:08.995
All the literature that I have come across over the years, which is related to the postabortion syndrome,

00:05:08.995 --> 00:05:14.479
was not even close to everything that I encountered in working with these women

00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:16.699
over the years.

00:05:16.699 --> 00:05:23.398
These were heavy guilt, panic attacks, insomnia, great depression,

00:05:23.398 --> 00:05:29.076
discord in the family, a sense of unworthiness, fears,

00:05:29.076 --> 00:05:35.435
great, great fears, of the death of a living child, of never being able to get pregnant again,

00:05:35.435 --> 00:05:39.672
of the fact that God would punish the mother, that she is under some kind of curse,

00:05:39.672 --> 00:05:46.044
the development of various addictions, whether it is alcoholism, drugs,

00:05:46.044 --> 00:05:52.542
eating disorders in the positive sense such as overeating,

00:05:52.542 --> 00:05:56.833
to the negative sense, i.e. depriving the body of food,

00:05:56.833 --> 00:06:00.434
even reaching anorexia, bulimia,

00:06:00.434 --> 00:06:06.122
enormous feelings of anger, hatred and so on.

00:06:06.122 --> 00:06:10.959
So these are all big, huge and heavy consequences that women face.

00:06:10.959 --> 00:06:15.729
What is also very, very devastating, and in fact too sad,

00:06:15.729 --> 00:06:21.137
is that many women who have gone through the experience of abortion have even attempted suicide.

00:06:21.137 --> 00:06:28.296
I actually met women who had scars from hanging, from cutting their veins,

00:06:28.296 --> 00:06:35.769
from taking too many pills and trying to kill themselves that way.

00:06:35.769 --> 00:06:41.214
These are serious consequences and we deal with them every day in the Association,

00:06:41.214 --> 00:06:44.960
since more and more such women are contacting us.

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:51.250
What is beneficial, related to this program, is that the Lord is wonderful,

00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:56.971
that He wants to enter all the dark corners of the woman’s heart,

00:06:56.971 --> 00:07:01.170
where she buried her child and the decision to keep it,

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:04.043
where she buried perhaps even herself.

00:07:04.043 --> 00:07:10.383
The Lord enters that darkness with His light. He brings life inside.

00:07:10.383 --> 00:07:16.739
He actually brings the truth first, and that truth, with the help of the Holy Spirit, sets free.

00:07:16.739 --> 00:07:22.130
Everything that they go through in the program, which touches those eight units,

00:07:22.130 --> 00:07:29.904
actually eventually leads to them reaching freedom through forgiveness.

00:07:29.904 --> 00:07:33.741
That’s why the program is called "Forgiven and Set Free."

00:07:33.741 --> 00:07:38.737
The different ways that I mentioned earlier about how women can contact us

00:07:38.737 --> 00:07:42.164
are through our Facebook page "Oprostom oslobođene,"

00:07:42.164 --> 00:07:49.940
through our e-mail address oprostom.oslobodjene@gmail.com,

00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:55.491
through the phone number 0955489645.

00:07:55.491 --> 00:08:02.079
Each of them is welcome, we can talk about everything and they can come freely,

00:08:02.079 --> 00:08:05.114
really freely and in full confidence.

00:08:05.114 --> 00:08:11.892
One of the other very important things about the program is that the program offers complete discretion.

00:08:11.892 --> 00:08:14.354
We organize it in smaller groups,

00:08:14.354 --> 00:08:19.983
so that all the people who come can really tell their story in, so to speak,

00:08:19.983 --> 00:08:25.875
controlled, checked and full of trust conditions.

00:08:25.875 --> 00:08:31.153
Mothers who carry the consequences of their abortion come at the beginning in some extreme 

00:08:31.153 --> 00:08:37.426
fear, shame, embarrassment, in some restlessness, and then as time passes,

00:08:37.426 --> 00:08:42.096
as the word of God begins to slowly open, melt and permeate them,

00:08:42.096 --> 00:08:46.543
they are happy when the moment comes for a big conversation,

00:08:46.543 --> 00:08:50.944
that is, for group discussion and sharing of life experiences.

00:08:50.944 --> 00:08:57.130
No abortion decision has ever been the same.

00:08:57.130 --> 00:09:01.437
No matter what the reasons may be, say, economic,

00:09:01.437 --> 00:09:05.356
or that the mother does not have support, or that she is afraid of how she will go on,

00:09:05.356 --> 00:09:09.658
or that she thinks that she herself is not worthy enough to be a mother and similar,

00:09:09.658 --> 00:09:12.023
no two reasons are equal.

00:09:12.023 --> 00:09:18.577
For this reason, it is necessary for them to tell their story, to verbalize their pain,

00:09:18.577 --> 00:09:24.379
to share with each other what they experienced and the reason why they decided to do something

00:09:24.379 --> 00:09:30.428
or why something happened to them, and after that they simply feel much better.

00:09:30.428 --> 00:09:36.000
They give each other advice on how to deal with something further

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.449
and then they can move on living after that.

00:09:38.449 --> 00:09:43.249
What we also offer them in this program, and without which we could not possibly do it,

00:09:43.249 --> 00:09:46.973
are the sacraments of our holy Catholic Church.

00:09:46.973 --> 00:09:51.248
Through the program, women prepare for a big confession.

00:09:51.248 --> 00:09:57.943
We have priests who conduct a spiritual conversation with them, as long as they need it,

00:09:57.943 --> 00:10:02.822
ask them whatever questions they need about their baby and so on.

00:10:02.822 --> 00:10:06.671
They simply make it even easier for themselves through confession.

00:10:06.671 --> 00:10:10.540
We also have adoration, we also have holy masses through the program,

00:10:10.540 --> 00:10:14.199
we sometimes also have the anointing of the sick.

00:10:14.199 --> 00:10:23.558
In general, all these Church blessings that our Church offers

00:10:23.558 --> 00:10:29.299
help women even more to feel accepted and loved.

00:10:29.299 --> 00:10:34.772
What is also important to say, when women call to come,

00:10:34.772 --> 00:10:41.691
they usually think: "maybe it’s too early, it’s been two weeks since I had a miscarriage,

00:10:41.691 --> 00:10:46.571
or it was a long time ago, I don’t remember anything, should I come at all."

00:10:46.571 --> 00:10:50.755
Each of them is welcome and as soon as one of the mothers actually thinks about

00:10:50.755 --> 00:10:52.682
whether she should come or not,

00:10:52.682 --> 00:10:56.661
it is certain that she is invited and that the program will be useful to her.

00:10:56.661 --> 00:11:01.442
Women came to us two weeks after losing a child,

00:11:01.442 --> 00:11:03.616
whether it was through a miscarriage or not,

00:11:03.616 --> 00:11:07.890
and we also had several cases where mothers had an intentional abortion,

00:11:07.890 --> 00:11:13.499
under enormous pressure from family members, and after it they immediately heard about us

00:11:13.499 --> 00:11:17.742
and they immediately went to call because they saw that they would not be able to survive it alone.

00:11:17.742 --> 00:11:22.349
We also had mothers who were 70, 80 years old,

00:11:22.349 --> 00:11:25.599
and their abortions were perhaps 40 years ago.

00:11:25.599 --> 00:11:29.523
Their wounds are still very, very alive.

00:11:29.523 --> 00:11:36.667
They still remember the act they did because it was deeply etched in their memory,

00:11:36.667 --> 00:11:42.986
and they are actually aware that their daughter or their son,

00:11:42.986 --> 00:11:49.118
who could have been 40 years old, isn’t sitting next to them and enjoying all that life would have for them

00:11:49.118 --> 00:11:52.917
if the mothers had allowed them to live.

00:11:52.917 --> 00:12:01.042
So we save the souls of these mothers, we bring them to God’s light.

00:12:01.042 --> 00:12:05.346
We are actually the extended hand of our Lord who comes to them,

00:12:05.346 --> 00:12:10.756
who pulls them with ropes of love, and gives them everything they need.

00:12:10.756 --> 00:12:13.648
That is peace in the soul and that is joy.

00:12:13.648 --> 00:12:19.393
I can’t even describe the fate of the women who came.

00:12:19.393 --> 00:12:25.944
I can only say that the experiences they lived through are incredible,

00:12:25.944 --> 00:12:31.786
the moments they got while going through these spiritual exercises and how they actually,

00:12:31.786 --> 00:12:39.071
letting the Lord surprise them, experienced that He delighted them,

00:12:39.071 --> 00:12:44.721
with His love, forgiveness, acceptance, with His mercy

00:12:44.721 --> 00:12:49.875
and with His paternal concern for their hearts and for their souls.

00:12:49.875 --> 00:12:54.670
We go soul by soul, heart by heart of one mother

00:12:54.670 --> 00:12:58.007
and, in this way, we build a better and more beautiful world.

00:13:04.620 --> 00:13:12.254
The happiest thing for me is when a mother refers another mother to come to the program,

00:13:12.254 --> 00:13:15.767
who herself testifies that it was easier and better for her after the program,

00:13:15.767 --> 00:13:22.770
and who suggests her contacting us freely and that she would feel just as well after she passes the program.

00:13:22.770 --> 00:13:29.622
In this way, I would like to invite all mothers who may be watching this,

00:13:29.622 --> 00:13:34.519
who themselves have experienced a miscarriage, in any way that it happened,

00:13:34.519 --> 00:13:39.429
in fact the loss of their baby, to contact us freely, to write to us.

00:13:39.429 --> 00:13:44.592
If some of them were on the program, they can freely, as many of them already do,

00:13:44.592 --> 00:13:50.317
send us their testimony and, in that way, encourage other mothers,

00:13:50.317 --> 00:13:56.954
and we will further agree on how they can join us through these seminars.

00:13:56.954 --> 00:14:04.458
Below, in the description of our video, we will write how everyone can get in touch, what are our contacts.

00:14:04.458 --> 00:14:10.786
You can also follow us, as I already said, on the Facebook page "Forgiven and Set Free."

00:14:10.786 --> 00:14:15.481
Here, we publish testimonials and announce where all our seminars take place,

00:14:15.481 --> 00:14:20.235
so everyone is free to contact us.

00:14:20.235 --> 00:14:24.948
I would also like to make the same plea: if you know a person who has gone through that experience,

00:14:24.948 --> 00:14:30.594
if you have seen on her perhaps some consequences or some great sadness, some longing,

00:14:30.594 --> 00:14:36.669
some worry or similar, it can also be one of the symptoms of postabortion syndrome.

00:14:36.669 --> 00:14:40.433
Feel free to refer her to us and we will help her.

00:14:40.433 --> 00:14:42.823
We will do our best and she will definitely get better.

